TypedRateLimitingQueueWithConfig, and using Add() in event handlers, Get()/Done() in the worker loop, and AddRateLimited() for error handling.\n\nThe delaying_queue.go provides TypedDelayingInterface which is the base for rate-limiting queues, adding AddAfter(item T, duration) capability for delayed requeuing."
